snippet.textDisplay:
Sunan Ibn Majah 4020

It was narrated from Abu Malik Ash’ari that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said:
“People among my nation will drink wine, calling it by another name, and  musical instruments will be played for them and they will hear  females singing  (females will sing for them). Allah will cause the earth to swallow them up, and will turn them into monkeys and pigs.”
